## Cost Analysis & Recommendations

### Free Tier Options (Current)
1. **GitHub Pages**: Unlimited public repository hosting
2. **Surge.sh**: 200MB storage, custom domain support
3. **Firebase Hosting**: 10GB storage, 125K requests/month

### Upgrade Paths (If needed)
1. **Netlify Pro**: $19/month - 1,000 build minutes
2. **Vercel Pro**: $20/month - Unlimited deployments
3. **Firebase Hosting Pay-as-you-go**: ~$1-5/month for this traffic

